'''吉尔吉斯共和国国家银行'''（{{lang-en|'''N'''ational '''B'''ank of the '''K'''yrgyz '''R'''epublic}}，简称'''NBKR'''）是[[吉尔吉斯斯坦|吉尔吉斯斯坦]]的[[中央银行|中央银行]]，负责发行货币[[吉尔吉斯斯坦索姆|吉尔吉斯斯坦索姆]]。其属于非营利性质的独立[[法人|法人]]实体，对外代表[[吉尔吉斯共和国|吉尔吉斯共和国]]参与国际活动。

== 目标与职能 ==

=== 目标 ===

1997年7月29日发布的[http://www.nbkr.kg/index1.jsp?item=40&lang=ENG 《吉尔吉斯共和国国家银行法》]{{Wayback|url=http://www.nbkr.kg/index1.jsp?item=40&lang=ENG |date=20140419174034 }}规定了'''吉尔吉斯共和国国家银行'''的总体目标是通过实施适当的[[货币政策|货币政策]]来实现和维持[[物价|物价]]稳定；因此其首要任务是维持国家[[法定货币|法定货币]][[吉尔吉斯斯坦索姆|吉尔吉斯斯坦索姆]]的[[购买力|购买力]]，和保持国家银行支付系统的稳定运作<ref name="About1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nbkr.kg/index1.jsp?item=1&lang=ENG |title=Goals, Objectives and Functions of the National Bank |accessdate=2014-07-06 |author= |last= |first= |authorlink= |coauthors= |date=2010-10-14 |year= |month= |format= |work= |publisher=National Bank of the Kyrgyz Republic |pages=1 |language=en |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419014700/http://www.nbkr.kg/index1.jsp?item=1&lang=ENG |archivedate=2014-04-19 |quote=The overall objective of the activity of the National Bank of the Kyrgyz Republic is to achieve and maintain stability of prices by means of implementing an appropriate monetary policy.The primary task contributory to attainment of the corporate objective of the bank is to maintain a purchasing power of the national currency, and safety and reliability of the banking and payment system of the republic. |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 职能 ===

为了执行其分配的任务，吉尔吉斯共和国国家银行依法独立管理，并从事以下活动<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nbkr.kg/index1.jsp?item=1&lang=ENG |title=The National Bank of the Kyrgyz Republic performs the following basic functions |accessdate=2014-07-06 |author= |last= |first= |authorlink= |coauthors= |date=2010-10-14 |year= |month= |format= |work= |publisher=National Bank of the Kyrgyz Republic |pages=1 |language=en |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419014700/http://www.nbkr.kg/index1.jsp?item=1&lang=ENG |archivedate=2014-04-19 |quote= |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=About1/>：
*1.制定，确定并实现金融政策；
*2.调控和监管[[银行|银行]]和[[金融|金融]][[信贷|信贷]]机构在法律许可下运营 ；
*3.研究、开发并实施统一的[[货币政策|货币政策]]；
*4.全权负责发行[[货币|货币]]；
*5.促进支付系统的有效运作；
*6.制定开展[[银行|银行]]业务，银行体系核算及报告的[[法规|法规]]。

== 组织结构 ==

吉尔吉斯共和国国家最高管理机构为董事会。董事会由七名全职工作的成员组成，成员由[[国会|国会]]选出再由[[吉尔吉斯斯坦总统|吉尔吉斯斯坦总统]]任命<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nbkr.kg/index1.jsp?item=40&lang=ENG |title=THE LAW OF THE KYRGYZ REPUBLIC on the National Bank of the Kyrgyz Republic |accessdate=2014-07-06 |author= |last= |first= |authorlink= |coauthors= |date=1997-07-29 |year= |month= |format= |work= |publisher=Kyrgyz Republic |pages=9章37节 |language=en |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419174034/http://www.nbkr.kg/index1.jsp?item=40&lang=ENG |archivedate=2014-04-19 |quote=The Board of the Bank of Kyrgyzstan shall consist of 7 persons. The members of the Board shall work full time in the Bank of Kyrgyzstan.The members of the Board shall include the Chief Executive Officer of the Bank of Kyrgyzstan, three deputies and members of the Board of the Bank of Kyrgyzstan, appointed by the President of the Kyrgyz Republic with regard for the representation of not more than seventy percent of the same gender. |deadurl=yes }}</ref>；
